data.value: Features Of This Software: 1. Supervisor, Manager and Owner can indivisually login. 2. Supervisor, Manager and Owner have different user interface. 3. Manager can create team and supervisor can supervise the team. 4. Manager can create new product and supervisor can update product report. 5. Employees and workers prodcutivity can easily trace. 6. Owner can see the products report and also employees report.
